                <p class="text-justify">Alitalia Airlines is the largest airline and flag carrier in Italy. The operates its services to over 34 scheduled domestic, European and intercontinental destinations i.e., a total of 97 destinations with a fleet size of 84 aircraft. From 2020, the airline is owned by the Government of Italy. </p>
