                <h2>Refund policy </h2>
                <p class="text-justify">According to <a href="https://www.faresmatch.com/alitalia-airlines-refund-policy.aspx">Alitalia airlines’ refund policy</a>, if you cancel your flight ticket within 24 hours of booking, you are entitled to get a full refund. If you fail to cancel the flight within the cancellation window, you will have to pay the cancellation charges that will be deducted from the refundable amount that you will receive. Also, if you fail to cancel your flight ticket, you will have to pay the penalty as per the cancellation policy of the airline. </p>
                <p class="text-justify">Further, the airline will process the refund to the source you used for making the payment. For instance, if you used a credit card, the amount will be credited to the same card. If you used a bank transfer, the amount will be processed to the same bank account. </p>
                <h3>Frequently asked question</h3>
